Title: Terrai Natural Products Neem Acne Bar
Description: Soaps are a very integral part of our daily lives, especially with all the dust and pollution around us. Thus a cleansing bar can be a practical and economical addition to any good skin care regimen. Bust most soaps available today, are made using soap noodles and contain animal fat and other chemicals that can leave your skin feeling dry and stretched after use. This is because they rob the skin of its natural oils and moisture. Scientifically, it has been proven that the human skin changes over time, which is why something as simple as changing your soap can make a big difference in results from a skin-care routine. Terrai soaps are formulated using Coconut Oil and other natural ingredients that are not harmful for the skin. Each soap is specially formulated and blended with natural active ingredients that ensure satisfactory results For people dealing with blemishes, a good cleanser is an important part of an anti-acne skin care routine.Terraisoap for acne control uses a gentle cleansing formula for skin with acne. Its hypo-allergenic formulation, made by blending Natural Extracts of Neem&Brahmi in a Clay (MultaniMitti) Base, works well on oily as well as skins with dry acne, as it does not leave the skin over dry. Glycerin, another key ingredient used in our formulation, has superior rinsing qualities. It cuts through the oil and rinses completely. The product contains no harsh additives, dyes or hardening agents. The clay base helps absorb the oil and dirt particles accumulated on the skin while Neem&Brahmi extracts ensure the skin remains clean and free of impurities. It is mild on the skin and does not clog pores, ensuring a healthy skin. Use: Use this product as a face and body wash during a bath or anytime you feel the need to effectively wash away the acne causing oil & other impurities that get collected on the skin due to pollution. Ingredients: Coconut Oil, Stearic Acid, Purified Water, Fuller?s Earth (Clay Pack), Tri-ethanolamine, Glycerine, SLS Powder, Neem, Brahmi Ext., Castor Oil, Titanium Di-Oxide, Coco-Betaine, Tea-Tree Essential Oil

Description: The celebrated house of Hermes presents Terre D’Hermes, a fragrance for the ultimate connoisseur of exquisite perfumes. A heady composition that is an alchemist between the ethnic and the modern, the luxury Eau de Toilette exudes an earthy tone that kindles the embers in the heart. Conceived in 2006, Terre D’Hermes is the magnificent creation of famed perfumer, Jean-Claude Ellena. Made for the man of the earth, he is one who believes in toiling hard for the fruits he desires. His strong gait reflects his no-nonsense attitude as does his strong brow and his straightforward smile.  For the discerning male who revels in the freshness of a fragrance so delicate, the opening notes bring about a wave of orange and grapefruit. Pepper and pelargonium hide in the heart even as they fade away to give way to the commingled accords of patchouli, cedar, vetiver and benzoin. The woody and the fruity accords flirt sweetly to create a swirling vivacity. The palpable voluptuousness of the fragrance is captured in a square, transparent flacon that seems to explain the simplicity of the most complex of emotions. Spritz on the lightness of the air that counterbalances the weight of the world with Terre D’Hermes.
